For instructions, see:

	http://zero-install.sourceforge.net/

But roughly:

* Create a new 'zeroinst' user (or just reuse your own user ID for testing)

* Install:

	$ ./configure --with-user=zeroinst
	$ make
	$ su
	# make install

* Mount:

	# mount /uri/0install

* Run helper (as 'zeroinst' user). Leave it running...

	$ zero-install

* Explore /uri/0install:

	$ cd /uri/0install/zero-install.sourceforge.net
